- **type:** `default`|`danger`|`warning`|`success` *default:* `default`
- **isActive:** toggle state `false`|`true` *default:* `false`
- **onDismiss:** action to call on dismiss
- **onAutoDismiss:** action to call when it is dismissed by the timer
- **dismissAfter:** seconds after which to dismiss the alert
